      "title": "Uncommitted Entries (lastLogIndex \u2212 commitIndex)",
      "description": "Entries written to the leader log but not yet committed by a quorum. Derived from lastLogIndex \u2212 commitIndex. When this approaches 200 (uncommitted-entry-count-to-reject-new-appends), the leader will start rejecting new writes. A sustained non-zero value under load is normal; a value climbing toward 200 with no recovery is critical.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 41,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 8
